{"tid":1279744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致最前線既勇武派","createTime":"2019-07-02T17:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T18:31:29.000Z","uid":27670,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"592fd20334161c02481380518e420210dd6bde66","tid":1279744,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:51:07.000Z","msg":"利申唔係分化<br />\n好唔想係大家咁團結既時候好似潑冷水咁<br />\n但係真係好重要<br />\n<br />\n做得最前線既<br />\n自然危險性亦最高<br />\n所以發夢既時候請你地高度注意自身私隱<br />\n要記住 其實有機會有鬼混入左去你地度影相<br />\n事實今日亦都真係有照片流出<br />\n呢樣先係最難防 因為佢同得你進行高危活動 大家既互信度會好高<br />\n但係唔好忘記 如果佢係鬼 跟你衝佢唔會有事<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>口罩呢條底線真係要企硬唔好除</strong></span><br />\n即使係記者都唔好 冇人知會唔會有freelance記者係藍底<br />\n唔係叫你地唔好信人 但係私隱要保障好<br />\n記住 你地係夢遊人士入面既稀有戰力<br />\n千其唔好貪一時方便而令自己陷入危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193601f7b848ef7ededf5c456a0156c675ffdf0b","tid":1279744,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:54:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3d6b644fc3b6967a3a8249a770995233487797ba","tid":1279744,"uid":272143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:57:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b6bf9367a9587678b88fb85c608bd5228f62df4a","tid":1279744,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:58:04.000Z","msg":"收到巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4c54261f1e5d4d209f5be89857a536ed6ececa","tid":1279744,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:58:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cd85917a34328b790cd6f6766a773b677c645bb3","tid":1279744,"uid":188256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:02:49.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我哋一個都不能少啊"},{"pid":"75ac04c874c2cb170c541dbc44fb1aa031978af2","tid":1279744,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:04:21